---
title: Garlic & Herb Seared Salmon with Leek Dauphinoise Potatoes & Garlic Greens
description: It’s fish tonight and on the menu we have salmon, seasoned and seared to tender perfection. Believe it or not, the star of
the show hasn’t even been introduced yet - layers of potato and leek are cooked in a creamy, cheesy sauce for the ultimate
accompaniment which is really the main event!
